Akahise
Abashakashatsi bavuga y´uku Uburundi bwamyeho nk´igihugu c´ikukiye kuva mukinjana ca 16.Mu 1903 niho c´atakaza intahe y´ukwikukira igihe hashikiye abadagi.Haheze ingwano y´isi yose y´ambere caciye cegukira igihugu c´ububiligi.Baciye bagifatanya n´igihugu cu Rwanda:Rwanda-urundi.Kuwa 1 Mukakaro 1962 niho casubira kuronka intahe yaco y´ukwikukira irondewe n´umuganwa Rwagasore Louis.Yarumukuru w´umugambwe wabadasigana UPRONA.

